                    <li><strong>Configuration:</strong> ________________________________</li>
                    <li><strong>Team Training:</strong> ________________________________</li>
                    <li><strong>Productivity Monitoring:</strong> ________________________</li>
                    <li><strong>Review Schedule:</strong> _____________________________</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="alternative-recommendations">
                <h4>Alternative Recommendations (if no plugin selected)</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>☐ Custom PyCharm live templates for .tt files</li>
                    <li>☐ Enhanced snippet library for Catalyst patterns</li>
                    <li>☐ Improved team documentation and examples</li>
                    <li>☐ Manual productivity workflow optimizations</li>
                    <li>☐ Regular review of new plugin releases</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

